{"tid":632860,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人嘅自卑係黎自另一半","createTime":"2018-04-17T19:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T05:44:25.000Z","uid":156122,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0bbc46834b56911494eda91362fcdd8d00f1a4da","tid":632860,"uid":156122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T19:24:37.000Z","msg":"一齊咗之後每一日都覺得好自卑<br />\n基本上冇一日係開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自卑唔係因為佢太好<br />\n而係佢覺得我冇樣好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f352deea31c751e99d05a24eaa32c344071de93e","tid":632860,"uid":162491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T19:25:51.000Z","msg":"覺得你唔好咁又一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d31515e6db80c969320e2c61f9662c35c748772","tid":632860,"uid":156122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f352deea31c751e99d05a24eaa32c344071de93e","tid":632860,"uid":162491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T19:25:51.000Z","msg":"覺得你唔好咁又一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T19:27:33.000Z","msg":"一齊個陣仲覺得我有啲野好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗佢而家應該後悔到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9a02a49dfe3306b79bd9786b0b8d04647025f9","tid":632860,"uid":54239,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T19:35:44.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n同ex一齊嗰陣成日俾佢彈我呢樣嗰樣<br />\n搞到個人勁唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n積左好多負能量<br />\n本身已經唔係有自信嘅人<br />\n俾佢搞到愈黎愈自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一排頹到連打扮都廢事<br />\n自卑到覺得自己打扮左都係柒<br />\n然後又唔想出街見人<br />\n<br />\n而家分開左<br />\n反而中意返扮靚<br />\n發覺原來打扮根本唔係為左取悅任何人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而係一樣可以令自己開心同有自信嘅生活方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc226c3a8aa1aaa12e8d248f12dc7ceccff8d91e","tid":632860,"uid":156122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8a9a02a49dfe3306b79bd9786b0b8d04647025f9","tid":632860,"uid":54239,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T19:35:44.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n同ex一齊嗰陣成日俾佢彈我呢樣嗰樣<br />\n搞到個人勁唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n積左好多負能量<br />\n本身已經唔係有自信嘅人<br />\n俾佢搞到愈黎愈自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一排頹到連打扮都廢事<br />\n自卑到覺得自己打扮左都係柒<br />\n然後又唔想出街見人<br />\n<br />\n而家分開左<br />\n反而中意返扮靚<br />\n發覺原來打扮根本唔係為左取悅任何人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而係一樣可以令自己開心同有自信嘅生活方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T19:40:34.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日比人彈<br />\n有時有啲野我知我係唔好 我認呀<br />\n但我自己知原因知點解唔好<br />\n講佢都唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢鐘意個髮型 叫我轉<br />\n轉完叫佢比下意見<br />\n又話唔知 又話冇乜特別 唔係柒嘅<br />\n講到尾 我係同佢心目中個啲「靚仔」唔同樣架啦<br />\n我係carry唔到架啦 鬼叫我柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日早成粒鐘起身gel<br />\n而家唔撚搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正佢都冇意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66f8890cdf50b0fb12a18eaa32f1c27b456e80d","tid":632860,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T21:03:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73a257bd39a37a32f85f4020d86707fe888b675c","tid":632860,"uid":20914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T21:12:15.000Z","msg":"又唔分手又要呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im